text: Edgardo Berdeguer (born 29 January 1954) is a Puerto Rican archer. Berdeguer competed at the 1976 Summer Olympics.Edgardo BerdeguerEdgardo BERDEGUER ==References== Category:1954 births Category:Living people Category:Puerto Rican archers Category:Olympians for Puerto Rico
